name: Polycom-directory
body:
### Welcome to the Polycom Directory Demo Project.
I created this as a place where we can collaborate on the code for this project.  Also to experiment with GitHub as a way to work with AMX code.

```
$ cd your_repo_root/repo_name
$ git fetch origin
$ git checkout gh-pages
```

### Authors and Contributors
Eric J Lewis: eric.lewisATalliancetel.com
